		<img src="http://www.linkedin.com/img/webpromo/btn_in_20x15.png" 
		width="40" height="30" alt="View Tammy Portnoy's LinkedIn profile" 
		style="vertical-align:middle" border="0"></span></a>

<a href="/rss"><img src="/images/feed-icon-28x28.png" height="30" width="30" style="vertical-align:middle"></a>
